@NODE "What" "What is it?"
WHAT IS IT?
---------

This is a little x-mas present for all Amigans. 
You can decorate your own christmas-tree with a lot of items (presents, candles, sweets etc).
Have fun and a merry christmas!
@ENDNODE
@NODE "Usage" "Usage"
USAGE
------
Well, this is not a program. It is just a simple picture. Load 'XMAS99.pic'  in a paint-program 
(i.e PPaint) and you get a very nice christmastree to decorate. 
On the right side of the picture, there are a lot of different items, which you just have to cut out with 
the brush-function and place them on the tree.

I have included some - already - decorated - christmas trees - examples of me, 
my girlfriend and her son.

Have a look. It's easy and fun!

- You need a high resolution to display all the items (800x600)
- Graphicscard recommended
- For the icons to display you need OS3.5
@ENDNODE
@NODE "Who" "Who made it?"
WHO MADE IT?
